1
00:00:25,275 --> 00:00:28,111
Professor Baek, I look forward to working with you this year.

2
00:00:28,111 --> 00:00:29,779
Even though you're a part-time lecturer,

3
00:00:29,779 --> 00:00:32,407
it'll be a great help for your full-time appointment.

4
00:00:32,407 --> 00:00:34,951
Let me know anytime if you need anything.

5
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:53,344
I really am lucky, aren't I?

6
00:00:53,344 --> 00:00:55,138
It's been a while, Teacher.

7
00:00:56,931 --> 00:00:58,808
Yoon Jaeon?

8
00:00:59,851 --> 00:01:03,313
1 Year Ago

9
00:01:03,313 --> 00:01:06,483
You can solve it by plugging in this formula.

10
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:08,902
I taught you this last week,

11
00:01:08,902 --> 00:01:09,986
you're not paying attention, are you?

12
00:01:11,529 --> 00:01:12,864
I know.

13
00:01:12,989 --> 00:01:13,990
Then why can't you solve it?

14
00:01:19,913 --> 00:01:21,164
I have something on my mind.

15
00:01:21,331 --> 00:01:22,999
I think I already know what it is without hearing it,

16
00:01:22,999 --> 00:01:24,084
so just finish solving the problem.

17
00:01:24,667 --> 00:01:26,544
Your exam is just around the corner, you know?

18
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:29,631
Aren't teachers supposed to counsel their students too?

19
00:01:29,631 --> 00:01:33,051
Go to school and talk to your school counselor for that.

20
00:01:33,051 --> 00:01:35,011
I'm not a school counselor,

21
00:01:35,011 --> 00:01:36,513
I'm your private tutor.

22
00:01:37,347 --> 00:01:38,890
That's so harsh.

23
00:01:39,099 --> 00:01:41,184
I'm telling you, I can't even sleep these days.

24
00:01:41,184 --> 00:01:43,520
I can't focus on my studies either.

25
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,979
If my grades drop,

26
00:01:44,979 --> 00:01:46,523
you're the only one who loses.

27
00:01:46,523 --> 00:01:47,732
That's actually great.

28
00:01:47,732 --> 00:01:49,317
We've seen each other for three years,

29
00:01:49,317 --> 00:01:50,527
it's about time we stopped seeing each other.

30
00:01:56,616 --> 00:01:58,118
There's someone I like.

31
00:01:58,243 --> 00:01:58,868
I know.

32
00:01:58,868 --> 00:02:01,121
You've been talking about it for three whole years.

33
00:02:01,871 --> 00:02:03,498
Aren't you curious who it is?

34
00:02:04,666 --> 00:02:06,835
I'm not interested in kids playing at romance.

35
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:10,922
Go talk to your friends for dating advice.

36
00:02:11,756 --> 00:02:15,218
The person I like is an adult.

37
00:02:15,218 --> 00:02:18,096
How is this kids playing at romance?

38
00:02:19,305 --> 00:02:21,057
I don't know what that person did

39
00:02:21,307 --> 00:02:24,352
to have a kid like you obsessing over them.

40
00:02:31,568 --> 00:02:34,404
That person is you, Teacher.

41
00:02:34,404 --> 00:02:37,198
The teacher who doesn't even cut me any slack for being a kid...

42
00:02:37,198 --> 00:02:39,742
That's who I like.

43
00:02:54,382 --> 00:02:58,636
I'm telling you, I like you, Teacher.

44
00:02:59,429 --> 00:03:03,224
You've liked someone before, so you know.

45
00:03:03,224 --> 00:03:07,187
How you can't control your own feelings.

46
00:03:08,855 --> 00:03:12,192
I know you said our school was your goal,

47
00:03:12,192 --> 00:03:14,944
but I didn't expect you to actually get in.

48
00:03:20,158 --> 00:03:21,951
Teacher!

49
00:03:24,287 --> 00:03:26,748
Or is it Professor now?

50
00:03:27,999 --> 00:03:29,417
How may I help you?

51
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:32,170
Wow, feeling a bit distant, aren't we?

52
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:33,838
Why the formal talk all of a sudden?

53
00:03:34,631 --> 00:03:37,800
Because you're not the high school student I used to tutor anymore.

54
00:03:38,468 --> 00:03:39,719
Just act like you used to.

55
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:42,138
Drop the formalities.

56
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:43,389
How have you been?

57
00:03:43,848 --> 00:03:45,642
Has it been about a year?

58
00:03:47,727 --> 00:03:48,895
Has it?

59
00:03:58,529 --> 00:03:59,489
What?

60
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,367
You're coming to the welcome party too, right?

61
00:04:04,827 --> 00:04:06,329
I guess so.

62
00:04:06,329 --> 00:04:08,331
Since the full-time professor called for me.

63
00:04:08,957 --> 00:04:10,708
That must be so annoying.

64
00:04:12,961 --> 00:04:14,212
Can you leave if you have nothing else to say?

65
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:17,257
I have a lot of work to do.

66
00:04:17,757 --> 00:04:18,841
We haven't seen each other in so long,

67
00:04:18,841 --> 00:04:21,844
aren't you being too cold?

68
00:04:21,844 --> 00:04:23,846
I wasn't planning to go, but I guess I will now.

69
00:04:23,846 --> 00:04:25,515
Since you're going too.

70
00:04:37,568 --> 00:04:39,320
What is this?

71
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:41,114
Were you this interested in me?

72
00:04:41,114 --> 00:04:42,240
Enough to look me up?

73
00:04:42,448 --> 00:04:44,617
Professor Han asked me to.

74
00:04:56,045 --> 00:04:57,130
Where are you going?

75
00:04:59,299 --> 00:05:00,675
Class.

76
00:05:02,302 --> 00:05:04,762
Stay if you want.

77
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,315
Why?

78
00:05:15,315 --> 00:05:17,066
What now?

79
00:05:17,066 --> 00:05:19,027
Do you have something to say to me?

80
00:05:21,362 --> 00:05:24,866
How have you been?

81
00:05:24,866 --> 00:05:27,327
Did you completely get over that person?

82
00:05:28,953 --> 00:05:31,497
I'm sorry, Sunbae.

83
00:05:31,831 --> 00:05:35,418
I don't think I'll ever have those feelings for you.

84
00:05:35,543 --> 00:05:39,756
Please just stay as a good Sunbae to me.

85
00:05:40,965 --> 00:05:42,884
That's none of your business.

86
00:05:43,384 --> 00:05:44,886
How is it none of my business?

87
00:05:44,886 --> 00:05:46,596
It's about the person I like.

88
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:50,141
We're at school.

89
00:05:50,141 --> 00:05:51,601
Watch what you say.

90
00:05:53,144 --> 00:05:54,645
Me saying that I like you...

91
00:05:54,645 --> 00:05:56,064
Is that a weird thing to say?

92
00:05:56,314 --> 00:05:57,523
Yoon Jaeon.

93
00:05:57,857 --> 00:05:59,692
I like you.

94
00:05:59,692 --> 00:06:04,989
I still like you a lot, Teacher.

95
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,710
What are you doing right now?

96
00:06:19,212 --> 00:06:23,966
I got into the best school, just like I promised.

97
00:06:23,966 --> 00:06:27,428
You said you'd grant my wish if I got into a good school.

98
00:06:28,846 --> 00:06:30,264
I just said that.

99
00:06:30,264 --> 00:06:32,475
Don't look too much into it.

100
00:06:32,475 --> 00:06:34,602
And stop messing around now.

101
00:06:35,269 --> 00:06:37,897
I'm not messing around.

102
00:06:38,898 --> 00:06:41,067
The feelings you have right now...

103
00:06:41,067 --> 00:06:43,069
You're just imagining it.

104
00:06:43,111 --> 00:06:44,362
Because we've known each other for a long time,

105
00:06:44,362 --> 00:06:46,989
you're just confusing your feelings.

106
00:06:47,031 --> 00:06:49,200
Why do you get to decide that?

107
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,660
These are my feelings.

108
00:06:50,827 --> 00:06:53,454
I know them best.

109
00:06:53,746 --> 00:06:55,665
I like you, Teacher.

110
00:06:55,665 --> 00:06:58,042
I have, for the past 3 years.

111
00:06:59,210 --> 00:07:01,379
I've only had my eyes on you.

112
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:07,260
Yoon Jaeon.

113
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:10,847
Playing house with a kid...

114
00:07:11,597 --> 00:07:13,975
I have no intention of doing that.

115
00:07:25,903 --> 00:07:27,321
You said it yourself...

116
00:07:27,321 --> 00:07:31,075
that I'm not a kid anymore.

117
00:07:31,325 --> 00:07:35,329
So now, I'm going to like you as much as I want.
